          <Dialog>
            <ID>1</ID>
            <Name>dface</Name>
            <ShowTextParser>False</ShowTextParser>
            <Script><![CDATA[// Dialog script file
@S  // Dialog startup entry point
face:As I was talking to my friends, I got a sudden flashback. 
face:A time I almost forgot about, or more like my mind tried to make me forget that absurdity.
face:You know, I’ve been at many a Jam’s before (Or Game Jam’s for noobs). 
face:But nothing was as strange as that one Jam at that old cabin...
return
]]></Script>
            <DialogOptions />
          </Dialog>
